item.title: Meetups
item.description: There will be weekly meetups. You are encouraged to attend as many as you can but recordings will generally be availabe the day after the meetup. Join Zoom Meeting: https://albany.zoom.us/j/93697731603 Meeting ID: 936 9773 1603 One tap mobile: +16465588656,,93697731603# US (New York) Phone Number: +1 646-558-8656 US US (New York) Please note: Students who participate in this class with their camera on or use a profile image are agreeing to have their video or image recorded solely for the purpose of creating a record for students enrolled in the class to refer to, including those enrolled students who are unable to attend live.
